# What is a module

# Background:
# Take a look at the screenshot. Instead Screenshot, please review the following code

# Import the os module 
import os 

# Check the type of os 
print ("The type of os is: " type(os)) 

# Display the documentation 
print (help (os)) 


# Excercises
# Can you identify which of the following definitions accurately describes a module?
Option A: Reusable code that can be imported into other programs
Option B: A predefined operation that performs a specific task
Option C: A file containing code that runs from start to finish




Answer: Reusable code that can be imported into other programs